---
import Layout from '../../Base.astro';
import SimpleHero from '../../components/SimpleHero.astro';
import FeaturedArticles from "../../components/FeaturedArticles.astro";
import ServicesRelatedWork from "../../components/ServicesRelatedWork.astro";
import "../../styles/pages/_services-list.scss";

---

<Layout
	title='Social Media Content - Florida Marketing Agency'
	description='Showing up on social is not the same as being remembered. We create platform-aware content that gives your brand a consistent story and a realistic publishing rhythm.'
>
	<SimpleHero tagline='Content Creation Services' title='Social Media Content' description="Showing up on social is not the same as being remembered. We create platform-aware content that gives your brand a consistent story and a realistic publishing rhythm." lottieFile='social-media-content.json' />
	<div class='service-body'>
		<div class='wrapper wrapper--narrow'>
			<h2>Where teams get stuck</h2>
			<p>Most social channels do not stall because a business has nothing to say. They stall because production is inconsistent, the content is not built for the platform, or the team is constantly scrambling for the next post.</p>
			<p>That leads to a presence that feels reactive instead of intentional.</p>
			<h2>How we fix it</h2>
			<p>We build social content around the brand story, the platform, and the publishing rhythm your team can actually sustain. That usually means creating a healthy mix of formats instead of forcing every idea into the same template.</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Infographics</li>
				<li>Data visualizations</li>
				<li>Microcontent</li>
				<li>Motion graphics</li>
				<li>Photography</li>
				<li>Video</li>
			</ul>
			<p>We also help identify which platforms deserve the effort so the work supports business goals rather than just filling a calendar.</p>
			<h2>What moving forward looks like</h2>
			<p>If your team is tired of posting without momentum or scrambling to stay consistent, we can help build a content system that matches your bandwidth and gives the audience a clearer reason to keep paying attention.</p>
			<p><a href='/contact/' class='button button--green'>Plan Social Content</a></p>
		</div>
		<ServicesRelatedWork tag={72} />
	</div>
	<FeaturedArticles />
</Layout>
